    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚将取消对移民工人到沙特阿拉伯的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/indonesia-set-to-lift-ban-on-migrant-workers-to-saudi-arabia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚将签署一项协议，以使其长达十年的暂停措施在保证对海湾国家更严格的劳动保护之后，将公民送往沙特阿拉伯为家庭工人和正规部门雇员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/indonesia-set-to-lift-ban-on-migrant-workers-to-saudi-arabia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 08:10:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希娜说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/croat-pm-plenkovic-hospitalized-for-heart-procedure-hina-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州新闻社Hina报道说，克罗地亚总理安德烈·普伦科维奇（Andrej Plenkovic）周五晚上住院治疗“偶尔会出现良性性格的心律失常”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-15/croat-pm-plenkovic-hospitalized-for-heart-procedure-hina-says</guid>
